Text cleaner: how to make your raw textual data nice and tidy.

How do I use it?

1) Move data you want to clean in text_cleaner folder.
2) Open terminal
3) ./text_cleaner yourinput.file
4) "output" and "stats" files are produced in the same folder

v1.0
Basic data cleaning. 

v1.1
Added option to remove lines composed by one single alphabetic word.

v1.2
C program producing simple descriptive statitics. To be improved.

v1.3
C program slicing long sentences. Cutpoint preferrably adjustable to the mean sentence length reported in stats.

v1.4
Re-run awk script after slicing to make the output tidy.

